Headquarters Regions: Greater Philadelphia Area, Great Lakes, Northeastern US
Full Description: CytoVas is a life science company with a unique cell-based informatics platform, CLOUD CYTOMICS™, that is advancing precision medicine by providing clinicians and drug developers with actionable information on novel cellular markers of disease progression and individual treatment response. The company’s technology uniquely enables it to mine flow cytometry data to rapidly identify and automate interpretation of novel cellular biomarkers. This breakthrough approach enables clients to make critical decisions in their efforts to develop and deliver safer, more precisely targeted therapies for patients. CLOUD CYTOMICS™ is broadly applicable across therapeutic areas and disease states and used throughout all stages of drug development. CytoVas is currently working with partners to exploit the technology’s potential in Cardiovascular Disease, Type 2 Diabetes, Preeclampsia, Alzheimer’s, Acute Myeloid Leukemia, Psoriasis, Rheumatoid Arthritis, and Peripheral Arterial Disease. Future studies are planned in Traumatic Brain Injury. Founded by world-renowned experts in computational biology, flow cytometry and cardiology at the University of Pennsylvania, the Company is led today by an experienced management team and scientific advisory board with a track record of success. Privately held, CytoVas is well funded by primary investments from the American Heart Association, the National Institutes of Health and the University of Pennsylvania, and a partnership with Becton Dickinson Biosciences, a world leader in flow cytometry.

Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Florida Alcohol and Drug Addiction Treatment at Ocean Breeze Recovery At Ocean Breeze Recovery we are dedicated to assisting individuals and families that are affected by drug or alcohol addiction. We promise to help these individuals find new and better way of living life. We are here to help you or your loved one every step of the way. If you want to transform your life, the time to act is now. Ocean Breeze Recovery offers you everything that you need to begin a new, substance-free life. Our staff uses an integrated treatment approach that includes therapy as part of our treatment program. Through our program we are able to teach individuals how to: Transform their standard of living Maintain abstinence Build healthy relationships Get proper nutrition Get plenty of rest and exercise Manage problems effectively At Ocean Breeze Recovery Center for Alcohol and Drug Addiction Treatment in Florida, we undoubtedly have confidence in our treatment approach. We believe that this is not only the best way but the only way to ensure long-term drug and alcohol rehab success. We also believe that addiction does not need to be a life sentence and that it can be managed successfully when the right treatment approach is used. Treatment for Drug Addiction and Alcoholism in Florida Located in beautiful Pompano Beach, Florida, Ocean Breeze is fully licensed in the state, and its counselors are certified and licensed in their various fields. We are dedicated to assisting individuals and families that are affected by alcohol or drug addiction. We promise to help these individuals find new and better way of living life. We are here to help you or your loved one every step of the way. If you want to transform your life, the time to act is now. Ocean Breeze Recovery offers you everything that you need to begin a new, substance-free life. About Ocean Breeze Recovery We want you to know a bit about Ocean Breeze Recovery. Our mission is to transform hope into healing for individuals and families affected by alcoholism and drug addiction through our treatment facility. To succeed in this mission, our expert services are committed to staying up to date with the latest advancement and information related to drug and alcohol addiction, education, and prevention. Ocean Breeze Recovery’s addiction treatment philosophy has never changed. We are always available via phone or email to answer any of your questions or concerns. Licenses and Accreditation: Ocean Beach Recovery is licensed by the Florida Department of Children and Families. In addition, we are an approved education provider through the Florida Certification Board, the Florida Department of Education and the National Association for Alcohol and Drug Addiction Counselors (NAADAC). Ocean Breeze Recovery is firmly committed to endorsing the prevention of drug and alcohol abuse. We firmly believe that drug and alcohol addiction is a completely preventable disease. This is supported by results from a recent National Institute of Drug Abuse funded research study which showed that prevention programs involving families, schools, communities, and the media are extremely effective in reducing drug and alcohol abuse. However, we do understand that many events and cultural factors affect drug and alcohol abuse trends. When youths perceive drug and alcohol abuse as harmful, they reduce or eliminate their drug and alcohol intake. That is why Ocean Breeze Recovery believes that education and outreach are the keys to helping youth and the general public understands the risks of drug and alcohol abuse. To assure these efforts teachers, parents, medical and public health professionals must keep driving home the message that drug and alcohol addiction can be prevented by abstinence.

Description: FinalCode delivers persistent file security in an easy, scalable and cost-effective platform that applies encryption.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: Headquartered in San Jose, California and with a vision to provide users and organizations with easy, flexible and comprehensive way to secure files designed to be shared internally and externally – FinalCode has assembled an experienced, innovative team of cybersecurity experts and technologists to offer small-to-medium businesses, government agencies and large global enterprises a persistent means to secure sensitive files wherever they go. Conventional file security approaches provide access and usage controls within internal or cloud repositories and containers. They typically require file owners and recipients to share passcodes, utilize application-specific connectors, or have common systems and applications. And most Information Rights Management (IRM) systems require of IT staff considerable planning, infrastructure changes and on-going administrative investment. Not only are they difficult to expand within a company, they are challenging to invite external file collaborators. They disrupt business and user workflow… which why users often circumvent these systems and send files to others without adequate controls. FinalCode offers a file encryption and file-based enterprise digital rights management (eDRM) platform that is agnostic to file storage, distribution and content management. As such, FinalCode can work with popular applications, devices, cloud storage, content management systems, and collaboration tools. Offered as either a software as a service (SAAS) or on premise virtual appliance software , the solution can be flexibly deployed as needed for an individual, department, business project, or enterprise-wide. FinalCode offer persistent file protection with strong encryption and an extensive array of granular usage controls including file traceability and means to remotely delete files even after they have been distributed. More so, the approach preserves user experience by integrating within existing file sharing workflow and allowing the recipient to work in the applications they are used to. FinalCode for Box ensures persistent file access, usage control and deletion of files that are outside the secure Box container in a way that is seamless to Box collaborators. This SaaS add-on option for Box Enterprise and Business Edition users extends Box’s file governance to files leaving the secure Box repository. And by enabling file security that is directly invoked within the Box interface, FinalCode for Box combines tremendous usability with the convenience of fast, as needed deployment. Furthermore, since FinalCode file security is mapped to Box collaborator settings, users do not need to set their own security policy, it is done automatically.
Industry Groups: Information Technology, Privacy and Security, Software
